     The Applied Information Technology Division supports NASA Ames
     Research Center as well as the ARC CIO in the following areas of
     Information Technology (IT):
     * IT Security
     * IT Planning
     * Center-wide Networks and Communications Systems
     * Center-wide IT Notifications
     * IT H/W + S/W Acquisition & Development
     * Customer Services

